Dogs sleep
kilab-u namat-uu

Dogs chase cars
kilab-u tutarid-uu sayaar-a

I chase you
tutarid-tu-ka


Dogs eat
kilab-u yakul-uu

The dogs dont chase cars
al-kilab-u lan tutarid-a sayaar-a


I think that you know that dogs chase cars
hasib-tu 2anna 2araf-ta 2anna kilab-u tutarid-uu sayaar-a

I ask whether you know that dogs chase cars
talabt-u idha 2araf-ta 2anna kilab-u tutarid-uu sayaar-a

Cats and dogs chase cars
qitat-u wa kulab-u tutarid-uu sayaar-a

Dogs chase cars and cats chase dogs
kilab-u tutarid-uu sayaar-a wa qitat-u tutarid-uu kilab-a

Cats chase dogs and sleep
qitat-u tutarid-uu kilab-a wa qitat-u namat-uu

Do cats chase dogs
2a qitat-u tutarid-uu kilab-a

Hungry dogs eat
yakul-uu kilab-un jay-un

Dogs in the park eat
kilab-u fi hadiq-i yakul-uu